Kicker {R}

Draw a card. If the kicker was paid, instead flip a coin. If you win the flip, draw 2 cards; otherwise, draw none.

If Double or Nothing is in your hand when a subgame ends, you may reveal it. If you do, exile Double or Nothing and restart the subgame. (Exiled cards stay exiled.) Any player that loses this time also loses an additional game.

Equip {1}
Equipped creature has "{T}: Scry 2."
You may attach {CARDNAME} to creatures controlled by other players. If you do, you may only tap that creature after its controller laughed this turn.
